EmailTemplate.name: Email Bank Draft Form
EmailTemplate.subject: Coca-Cola Auto-Draft Form
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.Name},
If you would like to enroll your freestyle account in the Coca-Cola Auto-Draft program for product purchases or lease fees, please fill out the attached request form and fax it to secured fax# 404.253.5077. Please process this as soon as possible to allow for account changes.
Also, please alert your bank of the ACH ID# 1580628465 for Coca-Cola to avoid any security blocks.
We look forward to assisting you with your Freestyle purchases.
Thank you for your continued support and patronage.
